app_description: Transcribe your voice memos and videos with ease using Speech to Text AI Dictation. Our advanced speech recognition technology provides high quality transcriptions that are easy to read and edit. Main Features: Auto transcribe text while recording Import audio and video files for transcription Highlight key points for easy review Punctuate capitalize and break paragraphs automatically Differentiate between speakers Search text to quickly locate important information Playback at adjustable speeds Edit text to correct errors Convert recordings to various formats: MP3 M4A AIFC WAV and more Transcribe in real time with high accuracy when online Export to png txt word and other formats Supports 30 languages and dialects Import files from other apps and Dropbox Export raw text to your favorite text editing app Synchronize unlimited files with our app No ads! We take security and privacy seriously and will never transfer your data to third parties. You have full control to delete your data from your account.
